# instance-field

InstanceV field access + monomorphic method dispatch in a hot loop.
10k calls to a 2-field accessor — deliberately stresses the slow
InstanceV path (interp is far behind the codegen backends here).

```scalascript
case class Vec(x: Int, y: Int)

def normSq(v: Vec): Int = v.x * v.x + v.y * v.y

def workload(): Long =
  val v = Vec(3, 4)
  var sum = 0L
  var i = 0
  while i < 10000 do
    sum = sum + normSq(v)
    i = i + 1
  sum
```
